{"type": "article", "id": 56066, "title": "意大利版《Elle》改为周刊，以及，Balmain 最新广告启用虚拟模特 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2018-09-04T08:43:36Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 15116, "name": "Y-3"}, {"id": 52507, "name": "Elle"}, {"id": 4125, "name": "京东"}, {"id": 4803, "name": "JW Anderson"}, {"id": 8634, "name": "Supreme"}, {"id": 2002, "name": "Balmain"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 574557, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 38, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180904162957dqyNj4lPonwECHus.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/business-news/media/elle-italy-publish-weekly-former-monthly-1202782506/\" rel=\"nofollow\">意大利版《Elle》将从月刊改为周刊</a>&nbsp;</strong>|&nbsp;赫斯特集团意大利公司 9 月 3 日表示，从 11 月起，意大利版《Elle》将从月刊改为周刊。改版后，杂志主编将由《Gioia》主编 Maria Elena Viola 担任，《Marie Claire》原主编 Antonella Antonelli 则担任创意总监。赫斯特集团意大利公司 CEO Giacomo Moletto 表示，改版是考虑到周刊的增长潜力和空间比月刊更大。目前《Elle》在全球共发行 45 版，只有法国和意大利版为周刊。</p><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/business-news/human-resources/j-w-anderson-names-jenny-galimberti-as-ceo-1202782371/\" rel=\"nofollow\">JW Anderson 任命前 LV 高管 Jenny Galimberti 为品牌 CEO</a>&nbsp;</strong>| Gamlimberti 原为 Louis Vuitton 传播及活动总监。在 2015 年加入 LV 之前，她也曾在 Gucci、Dunhill、L’Oréal, Swarovski 和 Prada 等品牌出任高层。在另一份声明中，LV 任命前 Prada 高管 Stefano Cantino 继任&nbsp;Gamlimberti 之职。《女装日报》评论认为，这次变动再次体现出 LVMH 集团从内部培养高管候选人的倾向，以及由传播公关岗位负责人担任品牌 CEO 的行业趋势。</p><p><strong><a href=\"http://www.bbtnews.com.cn/2018/0904/264229.shtml\" rel=\"nofollow\">京东与山东如意集团签署战略合作</a></strong> |&nbsp;根据协议内容，双方将在品牌入驻、无界零售、金融、物流、智能供应链、京东云等业务板块展开合作，同时将共同发起成立“如意－京东时尚产业创新发展基金”，投资全球著名时尚品牌及孵化新锐时尚品牌等项目。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><strong><a href=\"https://qz.com/quartzy/1375838/dont-call-balmains-cgi-models-diversity/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Balmain 最新广告弃用真人模特，转而选用三位&nbsp;CGI 虚拟模特</a></strong>。<br></p><p>除了在 Instagram 已拥有 14.1 万粉丝的黑人模特 Shudu，另两位虚拟模特均由 Balmain 创意总监&nbsp;Oliver Rousteing&nbsp;创造。一位是仿照 David Bowie 形象创作的中国美人 Zhi，另一个是 Rousteing 理想中的法国女孩 Margot。</p><p>这一举动引来了两极分化的评论。一部分人认为这是虚拟世界多样性的进步，另一部分则认为这只是表面上的多样性，并指出虚拟模特剥夺了真人模特的工作机会。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904154725oRqhWvXIt2c3BO4d.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904154746FG8PenBtdywTSMLr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904154759tFXk8gS6y15wVQUo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904155044A3goBTHsGMx4Ie2F.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.itsnicethat.com/news/supreme-aw18-collection-mike-kelley-art-030918\" rel=\"nofollow\">Supreme 推出与已逝现代艺术家 Mike Kelley 合作的 2018 秋冬联名系列</a></strong>。</p><p>该系列选用了 Mike Kelley 最具有代表性的作品，如《More Love Hours Than Can Ever Be Repaid》、《The Wages of Sin》、《Ahh…Youth!》、《Reconstructed History》等。单品包括工装夹克、工装衬衫、丝绸衬衫、圆领卫衣、连帽衫、T 恤及滑板，将于 9 月 6 日在纽约、洛杉矶、布鲁克林、伦敦、巴黎门店及<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.supremenewyork.com/shop\" rel=\"nofollow\">官方网站</a>发售，随后于 9 月 8 日登陆日本。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904151717Qvy8z5Hp7wboX3KO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.249333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201809041517290XmUfgBzbY5nNq4v.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.249333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904151737WxKDdJ4hS83Pkmge.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.249333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904151746DMZOcdN4S7zxCjEw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904151817L4Cgc1YUOzE562fj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904151905LftK35vCdk0n8ml1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665746\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904151919y4IS8GAC1eVXHwWb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.778704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904151929guU7j2zqOTNmDLaW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904151938XqegNrjMZSY0mHbk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904151951XexHEmspqaOUT5lA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904152000V31SOaybWgQnZRLh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201809041520092PYZ0uSc7iV3KAvC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904152017v6fsYgbrzwq1OcWo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201809041520276iawsMRNSmIdgP3h.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904152041xEniWy6P0X1Mozmt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904152054zKCxMwf3bqDOB6sE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904152108NJphjI2kdrWGbYgZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"http://nowre.com/fashion/354924/y-3-2018-qiudongdapian-chapter-02-shichu/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Y-3 发布 2018 秋冬大片 Chapter 02</a></strong>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904155140D1ld7neUPOI2TH6c.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904155158SPJWrqeOFaHcopNX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904155211WkO47Hclbaf1IXBC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.599517\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904155220n4d8LWUoEIixFXqY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.599190\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904155230dgEOfYo2xKSMcyB3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.599675\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904155239EgpozKlSWykvaBHj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.599675\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904155253H93FMJ0GI8uNbZOV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.599675\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904155304GcdgxkJQKNu1LMS2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.599675\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904155313Y18JjgWdcRLXEBmw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.599675\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904155323pGUQzsaHNry5RbTB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong>伦敦摄影师 Francesca Allen 发布最新摄影集 Aya</strong>，拍摄对象是 23 岁的日本音乐人&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/aya_gloomy/?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Aya Gloomy</a>。</p><p>Francesca Allen 希望在这本影集中探讨女性成长：<a href=\"http://www.dazeddigital.com/art-photography/article/41176/1/this-photo-book-explores-japanese-girlhood-and-friendship-francesca-allen-aya\" rel=\"nofollow\">“少女感不是指年龄，而是一种精神状态。”</a></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904231126yARGCr8SXPikvlgo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.513718\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904155911g6KIVfTecroFDas8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.281536\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904155921PadWtNqTsC4u8jU3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.531667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904155927rik5Ah0UjXbL2sgo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.242500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904155933L8fINMiys2uZt1v3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.254167\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904155940yAP9lS87I6Z2baro.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.518333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904155952dwvDsgx1tIA9RhFL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.227500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904231153K9ko30HmgUljrCWq.png\" data-ratio=\"1.224382\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904231208r2PNHSg3VIWk1sLp.png\" data-ratio=\"1.224382\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904155958kh2HJ4cRUDmpbz7l.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904231256mnA1i37pUuotLe5E.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.520625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904160007dmOA4qgGayxUjE9s.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.807500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong>突尼斯籍加拿大摄影师&nbsp;Oumayma B Tanfous 拍摄了 10 位纽约新兴年轻艺术家</strong>，并将这个系列命名为“Akrav Kids”<em>，</em>希望籍此探究年轻人如何塑造影响了纽约这座城市。</p><p>“我觉得纽约当下的青年文化比上世纪 70 年代普遍流行的嗑药和性要多些东西。无论是通过设计服装或是做音乐，这一代年轻人对自身生活的把控力更强，在享受其中的同时又影响着社会文化。”Oumayma B Tanfous 在接受 <a href=\"http://www.dazeddigital.com/art-photography/article/41150/1/10-new-york-creative-youth-kids-ouma-b-tanfous\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dazed 采访</a>时说。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904161157kNI7Kq0LlDyWvuZ9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.400233\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904161228kL4bvKNVmhQE1UX5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.251111\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904161239YbXtcQJWVnB4M0iG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904161248ZO13bnFI7quCkWrf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904161259EK7mP8LzwqD9CZ0S.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904161306qei3ahHSNvFspfuQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.251111\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904161326AhfovQHl7qjdb1Kp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904161336eybsN7MK3qSBQELn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904161345FueJyh7R1cBqv30s.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904161358S1Qlengip7dUsCK4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.380898\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904161423bzy5RkeLUfIWrsh9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.251111\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904161416lZbW5PMRty0KXLqo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.400233\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904161430dm1bSXxaHrwZAqzJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904161445YxWuSsV63L0vaQHi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.403509\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904161453BXhYFHkzSNtJL2PI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>题图来自 <a href=\"http://nowre.com/fashion/354924/y-3-2018-qiudongdapian-chapter-02-shichu/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Y-3 2018 秋冬大片</a></p>"}